OL,3,CMeet the tram driver celebrating 50
OL,4,Cyears at the Douglas Horse Tramway
OL,6,FA tram driver is celebrating 50 years
OL,7,Fworking for the historic Douglas Bay
OL,8,FHorse Tramway.
OL,10,FPeter Cannon has worked for the
OL,11,Fheritage service since 1975,
OL,12,Fdedicating most of his life to keeping
OL,13,Fthe Isle of Man tradition on the rails.
OL,15,FHe said: "I just enjoy it! It's better
OL,16,Fthan working for a living!
OL,18,F"It was just a summer job really, and
OL,19,FI kind of grew into it - I wasn't
OL,20,Fexpecting to be here for 50 years!"
