OL,3,CMeet the tram driver celebrating 50
OL,4,Cyears at the Douglas Horse Tramway
OL,6,FThe heritage tramway has been in
OL,7,Foperation since 1876, and often draws
OL,8,Ftourists to the Douglas seafront for
OL,9,Fits unique traditional feel.
OL,11,FPeter confessed he was "not a horsey
OL,12,Fperson at first" but learned to love
OL,13,Fworking with them as time went on.
OL,15,FHe said: "They just kind of grow on
OL,16,Fyou, it's a strange thing really, you
OL,17,Fmiss them when you're not here."
OL,19,FPeter first joined the Tramway team in
OL,20,F1975, as a conductor aged 17.
