OL,3,CMeet the tram driver celebrating 50
OL,4,Cyears at the Douglas Horse Tramway
OL,6,FPeter has made countless trips up and
OL,7,Fdown Douglas Promenade, but says the
OL,8,F100th anniversary of the trams was a
OL,9,Fparticular highlight.
OL,11,FHowever he said there were "too many
OL,12,Fincidents to mention" and overall he
OL,13,Fhas "just had a lot of fun over the
OL,14,Fyears".
OL,16,FWhen Peter was asked whether it feels
OL,17,Flike 50 years of work, he said:
OL,18,F"Depends on the weather!"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
