OL,3,CMeet the tram driver celebrating 50
OL,4,Cyears at the Douglas Horse Tramway
OL,6,FHe concluded by saying: "There's a
OL,7,Fsaying isn't there, if you can find
OL,8,Fsomething that you like as a job you
OL,9,Fknow it's not like work is it? Well I
OL,10,Fsuppose you can say I've never done a
OL,11,Fdays work in my life."
OL,13,FThe Douglas Bay Horse Tramway has been
OL,14,Fin operation since 1876 - next year
OL,15,Fcelebrating its 150th year.
OL,17,FPeter said he looks forward to the
OL,18,FTramway marking the major milestone,
OL,19,Fand will work to keep the tradition
OL,20,Fgoing for as long as he can.
